frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature figures in red uniforms working on a large lemon tart. They appear to be using ladders and ropes to maneuver a giant lemon slice onto the tart's surface. The setting is playful, resembling a construction site with a culinary twist.
frames.description: The image portrays a creative and imaginative setting where tiny figures are engaged in what looks like a construction project on a lemon tart. The figures, dressed in red, are interacting with oversized lemon slices, giving the impression of a fantastical world where food and construction merge.

frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature workers in red uniforms assembling a lemon tart. The workers are carefully positioning large lemon slices on top of the tart, using ladders and ropes. The setting is playful and imaginative, blending culinary art with miniature craftsmanship.
frames.description: The scene is set on a wooden surface where a lemon tart is being 'constructed' by tiny figures dressed as workers. The tart is topped with large lemon slices, and the figures are actively engaged in placing and adjusting the slices. The background features whole lemons, adding to the citrus theme.
